<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148990" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="5">Further information can be found in the Help in <link href="text/shared/01/05030500.xhp" name="Borders"><emph>Borders</emph></link>. You can also find information on how to <link href="text/shared/guide/border_table.xhp" name="format a text table">format a text table</link> with the <emph>Borders</emph> icon.</paragraph>
